Short:    Converts FKey's config to A New MCP.config File
Author:   Bruce steers <bsteers@btinternet.com>
Uploader: http://www.btinternet.com/~bsteers/
Version:  2.0
Required: MUI, (: and MCP + FKey ;)



                         FKey2MCP_mui by Bruce Steers.

                This is a convertor that reads FKeys tooltypes,
              extracts the info and creates a new MCP.config file


           I have realy only made thig prog for some mui expierience

     the code probably sucks in neatness but i think it handles everything
       i have included the source (Amiga_E) so take a look if you like :)

